IZINKINGA zemihla ngemihla ezivela uma kukhona isihhlobo noma othandiweyo wakho kubukeka zizoshabalala njengemazolo ebona ilanga ngemuva kokuvulwa kwamahhovisi enkampani kamasingcwabisane KwaMagaba, elokishini eMpumalanga ngaseHammarsdale, entshonalanga yeTheku. ISizwe Sethu okuyinkampani yokungcwaba esabalele naso sonke isifundazwe, futhi abaphathi nabasebenzi bayo abaqikelelayo ukunikeza lowo mndeni odlulelwe yisihlobo umngcwabo osezingeni ngemuva kokuzwa izincumo zomphakathi ngomsebenzi omuhle ewenzayo igcine isithathile isinqumo sokuvula amahhovisi ayo kule ndawo esentshonalanga yeTheku. Amahhovisi asezitolo KwaMagaba ngaphesheya nje kwehholo lomphakathi, emgwaqeni omkhulu uSishi. Kusukela ngoMsombuluko kuyakuLwesihlanu kuvulwa ngo-8 ekuseni kuvalwe ngo-4 ntambama. NgeMgibelo kuvulwa ngo-8 ekuseni kuvalwe ngo-12 emini. Okwenze lomasigcwabisane wabanedumela emphakathini wakulendawo wafisa ukuthi ube namahhovisi kulendawo yindlela abasebenzi bawo abayikhombisayo uma benemicimbi yomngcwabo kulendawo asebeke bayenza. Abantu bangaqala ukuza kulamahhovisi bazozwa ukuthi ngakube wona yini le owenza ngayo ukugcina isethembiso njengoba isikhathi esiningi kuba nezikhalo ngomasingcwabisane okuhlanganisa ukungasigcini isikhathi, kanye nokungakwenzi lokho umuntu asuke evumelene ngakho nomasingcwabisane ngesikhathi ewujoyina. Ezimnandi zithi ezinsukwini ezimbalwa ezizayo kulindeleke ukuthi kube nesipesheli esizohlelwa umphakathi wakuleli lokishi uma uzojioyina. Lesi sipesheli asiqondene nomphakathi waseHammaradale kuphela, kodwa nabantu abakhele izindawo ezisondelene naleli lokishi bavumelekile ukuthi basondele isikhathi isikhathi sisekhona. Ngaphandle nje kwalokho miningi imihlomulo oyitholayo ngokuba yilungu leSizwe Sethu. Futhi noma ufuna ukuhlela umcimbi wokumbulwa kwetshe bakhona. Bayawaqopha amatshe amatshe amathun asezingeni eliphezulu. Ngeminye iminingwane ungashayela ku-0734825893 ngezikhathi zomsebenzi noma ushayele kulenombolo ethi, 0826765266 zikhathi zonke. Ikomkhulu lalo masingcwabisane lisePinetown, emgwaqeni uHill Street.